OL,6,FToday, on the three-year anniversary
OL,7,Fof Russia's full-scale invasion, his
OL,8,Fbody is still in the battlefield.
OL,10,FHis family are unable to lay him to
OL,11,Frest or say their final goodbyes.
OL,13,FIt took Helen, who has been diagnosed
OL,14,Fwith post traumatic stress disorder
OL,15,F(PTSD), months to tell her 11-year old
OL,16,Fson the news of his father's fate.
OL,18,F"I had to explain to my young child
OL,19,Fthat his father is dead," she told ITV
OL,20,FNews.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
