OL,6,F"I tried to explain to him that his
OL,7,Ffather is a hero because he gave his
OL,8,Flife for Ukraine. But my son wants a
OL,9,Fliving father, not a dead hero. He
OL,10,Fdoesn't understand why his father
OL,11,Fdied."
OL,13,FIt took Helen Hetmanenko months to
OL,14,Ftell her young son the news that his
OL,15,Ffather, Yura, had been killed
OL,17,FHelen has attempted to rebuild their
OL,18,Flives solo, enrolling Ihor in St
OL,19,FMary's Ukrainian School in Holland
OL,20,FPark, London, which supports over
OL,21,F2,500 displaced children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
