OL,6,FBut the psychological trauma of the
OL,7,Flast three years has taken it's toll
OL,8,Fon them both. A universal experience
OL,9,Fat St Mary's, according to the
OL,10,Fschool's headteacher.
OL,12,F"I think there is no Ukrainian child
OL,13,Ftoday who hasn't been either directly
OL,14,For indirectly impacted by war," Inna
OL,15,FHryhorovych told ITV News.
OL,17,F"Every Ukrainian child has suffered
OL,18,Ffrom trauma, and is continuously being
OL,19,Fretraumatised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
