OL,6,F"These children, although safe here
OL,7,Fand now physically, being kindly
OL,8,Fhosted by the British public, are
OL,9,Fstill carrying flashbacks and the
OL,10,Fimpact of this horrific war. And
OL,11,Fthat's the stamp on their life, for
OL,12,Fthe rest of their life."
OL,14,FInna Hryhorovych, headteacher of St
OL,15,FMary's School in London says Ukrainian
OL,16,Fchildren are being 'continuously
OL,17,Fretraumatised'
OL,19,FBut there is some light within the
OL,20,Fdarkness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
