OL,6,FThe walls of the classrooms are
OL,7,Fadorned with brightly coloured
OL,8,Fdrawings and banners promoting peace
OL,9,Fin the bright blue and yellow colours
OL,10,Fof the Ukrainian flag.
OL,12,FSt Mary's school also offers respite
OL,13,Fto refugees of all ages, including
OL,14,Fdance classes for their youngest
OL,15,Fstudents, to embroidery groups and
OL,16,FEnglish lessons for pensioners.
OL,18,FTetiana Mykytenko's husband is
OL,19,Ffighting in the front line in Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
