OL,6,FThe mother-of-five is among the more
OL,7,Fthan 300,000 Ukrainian refugees who
OL,8,Fhave sought safety in the UK since
OL,9,F2022.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FShe now worries that globally Ukraine
OL,17,Fis being forgotten, with comments from
OL,18,Fworld leaders such as the US President
OL,19,FDonald Trump causing her concern.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
