OL,6,F"The truth is being flipped, it's
OL,7,Fbeing flipped by the media and big
OL,8,Fleaders and that's heartbreaking
OL,9,Fbecause then we think the whole world
OL,10,Fis against us," she said.
OL,12,F"I want to believe that the whole
OL,13,Fworld would hear our words ...
OL,14,Feveryone needs to hear our pleas for
OL,15,Fhelp.
OL,17,F"Our country is very small compared to
OL,18,Fthe aggressor. We can't do much by
OL,19,Fourselves. We don't have enough
OL,20,Fammunition or people," she added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
