OL,6,FIn a show of support for Ukraine,
OL,7,Fleaders from Europe and Canada -
OL,8,Fincluding European Commission
OL,9,FPresident Ursula von der Leyen and
OL,10,FCanadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau
OL,11,F- attended a summit led by Ukraine's
OL,12,FPresident Volodymyr Zelenskyy.
OL,14,FProtests against Russia's continued
OL,15,Faggression have taken place in major
OL,16,Fcities across the UK, held together
OL,17,Fwith emotional memorials to Ukraine's
OL,18,Ffallen soldiers and civilians.
